Vendor Demonstrations 

Counter Measures, Inc.
A full demonstration of Countermeasures Inc. risk assessement software
will be  provided.   This package can quantitatively assess risk of any
data processing installation. This package is currently in use here at
the NASA Johnson Space Center.

Electronic Frontiers of Houston
Electronic  Frontiers of Houston will give a seminar on PGP (Pretty Good
Protection) file encryption software. They will speak on public and
private  key encryption, the proper use of PGP as well as encryption key
management and key servers.

LJK Software
LJK Software will demonstrate their software that performs centralized
security assessment of distributed VMS systems.  Amongst the features
shown in this software package, they will show how it will provide for a
separation of duties between those who implement security (idnividual
system security officers) and those who review that implementation (the
security staff).


